'''約翰卡羅爾大學'''（'''John Carroll University'''）是一所位於美國[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[克利夫蘭|克利夫蘭]]郊區[[大學高地_(俄亥俄州)|大學高地]]的私立[[天主教大學|天主教大學]]，主要提供本科生教育。<ref name="At a Glance">{{cite web | url = http://webmedia.jcu.edu.s3.amazonaws.com/pdf/JCUAR.pdf | title = 2011 Annual Report | publisher = John Carroll University | accessdate = 2012-07-02 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://sites.jcu.edu/magazine/2010/09/30/a-global-perspective/ | title = A Global Perspective | publisher = John Carroll Magazine | accessdate = 2011-11-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120519025141/http://sites.jcu.edu/magazine/2010/09/30/a-global-perspective/ | archive-date = 2012-05-19 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="Center for Global Education">{{cite web | url = http://www.jcu.edu/global/study | title = Center for Global Education | publisher = John Carroll University | accessdate = 2011-11-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111127043255/http://www.jcu.edu/global/study/ | archive-date = 2011-11-27 | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 2020年《[[美國新聞與世界報道|美國新聞與世界報道]]》將其列在“中西部地區大學”中的第2位。<ref name=USNews>{{cite web |url= https://www.usnews.com/best-colleges/john-carroll-university-3050 |title= Usnewsranking Rankings: Best Colleges |publisher= ''[[U.S._News_&_World_Report|U.S. News & World Report]]'' |year= 2020 |access-date= 2019-12-20 |archive-date= 2021-04-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210420110433/https://www.usnews.com/best-colleges/john-carroll-university-3050 |dead-url= no }}</ref>

==歷史==
[[Image:Jcu_tower.jpg|thumb]]
該大學由[[耶穌會|耶穌會]]成立於1886年，當時稱聖伊格內修斯學院（St Ignatius College），是一所男子學院。<ref name="Ohio Journal of Science">{{cite web | url = https://kb.osu.edu/dspace/bitstream/1811/23130/1/V086N3_051 | title = History of the Biology Department of John Carroll University | publisher = Ohio Journal of Science | accessdate = 2006-10-03 | archive-date = 2007-06-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070622201930/https://kb.osu.edu/dspace/bitstream/1811/23130/1/V086N3_051 | dead-url = no }}</ref> 1923年為紀念美国首位罗马天主教主教和大主教[[約翰·卡羅爾|約翰·卡羅爾]]而改現名，1935年搬至現址。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://cleveland.about.com/od/education/p/johncarroll.htm | title = John Carroll University | publisher = About, Inc. | accessdate = 2006-10-03 | archive-date = 2011-07-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110709161521/http://cleveland.about.com/od/education/p/johncarroll.htm | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

二戰期間，它是美國131所參加[[V-12海军学院培训计划|V-12海军学院培训计划]]的美國學院之一，為學生提供海軍軍事教育。<ref name="jc-v-12">{{cite web |url=http://sites.jcu.edu/veterans/ |title=Veterans Program |publisher=University Heights, Ohio: John Carroll University |last= |first= |accessdate=September 29, 2011 |year=2011 |archive-date=2012-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401233637/http://sites.jcu.edu/veterans/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 1968年9月男女共學，在21世紀初擴張。

